# Gym Database

![img](./database/er.PNG "GYM ER")

## Insert Exercise http://localhost:3030/exercises

```json
{
  "name": "Push-Up",
  "model": "3D Model_man",
  "animation": "Animation1",
  "note": "Standard push-up exercise for upper body strength",
  "status": true,
  "thumbnail": "data:image/jpeg;base64,"
}
```

## Insert User http://localhost:3030/user

```json
{
  "username": "john_doe2",
  "email": "john2.doe@example.com"
}
```

## Insert Schedule http://localhost:3030/schedule/user/1

```json
{
  "start_date": "2023-09-24",
  "days": [
    {
      "day_number": 1,
      "exercises": [
        { "exercise_id": 1, "order_number": 1 },
        { "exercise_id": 2, "order_number": 2 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "day_number": 2,
      "exercises": [
        { "exercise_id": 3, "order_number": 1 },
        { "exercise_id": 4, "order_number": 2 }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
